node.text:
This year has been challenging, life changing, and one we will never forget! Cheers to a new year full of health, hope, peace, and joy🥂❤️

2 winners will get a $100 shop credit for them + a friend!

How to enter:
1- Like + save this post
2- tag a friend below and write what you wish them for the next year. You can tag as many friends as you’d like, each separate tag is another entry!

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by mushie in Houston, Texas.

node.text:
⚡️GIVEAWAY⚡️
You can win a @mushie bundle + a year supply of @frigg_official in celebration of them reaching 20K followers🎉

How to enter:
1- like and save this post
2- follow @mushie and @frigg_official
3- tag friends below in separate comments. Each comment is another entry!

Winner announced Tuesday, open worldwide!

node.text:
Bundle of JOY Giveaway ✨
We are beyond excited to be partnering with so many incredible brands to spoil ONE LUCKY MAMA with $3,500 worth of baby essentials for their little bundle of JOY!! To enter to win this incredible giveaway, simply visit the link in @saranoniblanket bio! Make sure to like this post and tag all the mamas you know because you don’t want to miss out on this! 

Swipe through to see all the brands involved. Giveaway ends September 25th 11:59pm MT and is open to US residents only. Must be 18 years or older to enter. Winner will be announced Monday September 27th. This giveaway is not administered by or associated with Instagram. Please be aware of SPAM accounts- the winner will be announced on each brand’s official Instagram page only. GOOD LUCK!
